  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/DiskArbitration\/DADiskMountOptions\ncrawled: 2026-03-10T15:25:15Z\n---\n\n# DADiskMountOptions\n\n**Type Alias**\n\nOptions for DADiskMount().\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\ntypealias DADiskMountOptions = UInt32\n```\n\n## Constants\n\n- **kDADiskMountOptionWhole**: Mount the volumes tied to the whole disk object.\n\n## Data Types\n\n- **DADiskClaimOptions**: Options for DADiskClaim().\n- **DADiskEjectOptions**: Options for DADiskEject().\n- **DADiskOptions**: Options for DADiskGetOptions() and DADiskSetOptions().\n- **DADiskRenameOptions**: Options for DADiskRename().\n- **DADiskUnmountOptions**: Options for DADiskUnmount().\n- **DAReturn**: A return code.\n\n",
